CEO RYU SEOK OFF-SITE SCHEDULE

38:49.869 --> 38:51.203
What'll you do now?

39:00.546 --> 39:02.256
Gonna be rough from here on out,

39:02.923 --> 39:04.925
so you do what you feel is right.

39:09.680 --> 39:11.766
Are the physical examinations
going well?

39:11.766 --> 39:13.559
Yes, the explosions scared them,

39:13.559 --> 39:16.062
but more of them
are getting exams without problems,

39:16.062 --> 39:18.606
which makes it a bit more popular
as we proceed.

39:23.944 --> 39:26.864
<i>Refugees who have finished
registering their personal information</i>

39:26.864 --> 39:30.284
<i>will receive a basic physical examination,
including measuring height and weight,</i>

39:30.284 --> 39:32.453
<i>and receive a comprehensive vaccine shot.</i>

39:32.953 --> 39:36.082
<i>The comprehensive vaccine was created
by Cheonmyeong Pharmaceuticals</i>

39:36.082 --> 39:39.710
<i>in consideration of the weakened
immune system and health of refugees.</i>

39:39.710 --> 39:42.838
<i>The vaccine has undergone a thorough range
of clinical trials and tests</i>

39:42.838 --> 39:44.965
<i>to prove its safety and efficacy.</i>

39:47.176 --> 39:48.010
<i>Refugees will...</i>

39:48.010 --> 39:50.012
Oh, there's more than I thought.

39:50.012 --> 39:52.807
I'm sure it's because we had announced
that you'd be here.

39:56.227 --> 39:58.729
<i>Once all refugees
have completed their examinations,</i>

39:58.729 --> 40:02.316
